description:
In this presentation we showcase a Proof of Concept (PoC) in the framework of ARTES ISAAC &quot;Life Science &amp; Healthcare Tech&quot;. 

 In particular, we present the method for regional quantitative analysis of fat deposit in the epicardium, which, as other visceral fat localizations, is correlated with cardiovascular disease, cardiovascular risk factors and metabolic syndrome. 

 &nbsp;

